MySQL::Admin version 0.84

Just a MySQL administration Web-App.

Copy the whole tarball to your DocumentRoot.

Open install.html in your Browser.

or edit cgi-bin/config/settings.pl

Open index.html in your Browser.

Delete cgi-bin/install.pl

Delete install.html

look at https://sourceforge.net/projects/lindnerei/ for further Details.

You can also install this Web-App via cpan 

cpan MySQL::Admin

INSTALLATION

To install this modul you need a webserver (Apache).
mod_perl and GD(Authen::Captcha) are optional.
MySQL Server.
Mysql user  and Database.

To install this module type the following:

perl Build.PL
  ./Build
  ./Build test
  ./Build install
  ./Build testdb

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libaries:
  Test::More >= 0.7,
  Module::Build >= 0.2808,
  HTML::Menu::TreeView >= 1.04,
  DBI >= 1.50,
  CGI >= 3.29,
  MD5 >= 2.03,
  URI >= 1.40
recommends
  Authen::Captcha
  1.024

